<p></p>
<h3>Where do I Begin?</h3>
<p>Students who meet the <a href="x43410.xml">admission requirements</a> can <a href="http://www.byui.edu/admissions/what-type-of-applicant-am-i/new-freshman">apply</a> to be directly admitted into an online degree program. These students will start by taking&nbsp;<a href="x43378.xml">GS111</a>, a one credit online orientation course&nbsp;offered every block. This course prepares students to succeed online and charts a course to graduation. Pathway students who complete Academic Start do not need to take GS 111.</p>
<p></p>
